08/10/2002
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Chief of General Staff Gen Nikola Kolev welcomed his Turkish counterpart Gen Hilmi Ozkok to Sofia on Monday (7 October). 
Unofficially, they have discussed positions on a possible operation against Iraq, but both expressed hopes the conflict could be resolved peacefully. 
During his two-day visit, Ozkok is also to meet with President Georgi Parvanov and Defence Minister Nikolay Svinarov. 
(Trud - 08/10/02; BTA - 07/10/02)
